{"id":301908,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-长沙访民俞腊梅等8人被非法限制人身自由/","date":"2013-07-02T17:32:53Z","modified":"2013-07-02T17:32:53Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙访民俞腊梅等8人被非法限制人身自由近40小时","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员徐闯报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，刚刚走出派出所的长沙访民俞腊梅致电本网信息员称：她于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>被望月湖街道办的综治人员强行从火车站拖走，她们报警后车站派出所给她做了笔录，通知岳麓分局望月湖派出所将她接回，关押在望月湖派出所内，直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点左右才获得自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">      </span></div>\n<div><span>据俞腊梅说：一同被关押的还有另外</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>位访民，她们都是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日去北京被截访的拆迁户，分别是：刘志方（男）、刘福云（男）、陈有余</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span><span>女）、姜惠珍（女）、杨惠芳（女）、戴晓安（女）、胡自兴、段小安。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">   </span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">      </span></div>\n<div><span>俞腊梅介绍说：她们都是长沙强拆受害者，自家的合法房屋被非法强拆后，一直得不到合理赔偿，本来打算七一期间去北京上访，谁知还没走出长沙就被截访抓了回来，并非法限制人身自由近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>小时。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>俞腊梅电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13142221308</span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]